This is a brand page for the SPUD trademark by Arovia, Inc. 
                                in Houston, TX, 77288.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this SPUD trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Arovia, Inc. of the SPUD trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the SPUD trademark.
                           


Status Update!
                          On Monday, June 26, 2017, status on the SPUD trademark changed to STATEMENT OF USE, REGISTRATION REVIEW COMPLETE.
                        






On Monday, December 14, 2015,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        SPUD by 
                        Arovia, Inc., Houston, TX  77288.
                        The USPTO has given the SPUD 
                        trademark serial  number of  86847703.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is STATEMENT OF USE, REGISTRATION REVIEW COMPLETE.
                        The correspondent listed for SPUD is 
                        
                        
                                            JOHN DAVIS of 
                                            Bibby, McWilliams & Kearney, PLLC,  410 Pierce St., Suite 241, Houston, TX 77002 
                                .
                            The SPUD trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Computer & Software Products & Electrical & Scientific Products
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for SPUD 
                            is Computer monitors; Computer screens; Flat panel display screens; Flexible flat panel displays for computers; Video monitors. 
                            





